%20your%20patience%20yesterday%20with%20the%20unexpected%20technical%20product%20issues.%20As%20customer%20zero%2C%20this%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20learn%20and%20quickly%20make%20improvements.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20Satya%20shared%20at%20the%20recent%20Employee%20Town%20Hall%2C%20our%20success%20as%20a%20company%20depends%20on%20our%20relevance%20in%20year%2051%20and%20beyond%20-%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20innovation%2C%20the%20products%20we%20deliver%2C%20and%20the%20impact%20we%20have%20for%20our%20customers%20and%20partners.%20With%20that%2C%20our%20focus%20remains%20on%20enabling%20high%20performance%20to%20achieve%20our%20priorities%20spanning%20security%2C%20quality%2C%20and%20leading%20Al.%20This%20focus%20and%20our%20growth%20mindset%20encourage%20excellence%2C%20motivates%20us%20to%20push%20ourselves%20through%20challenges%2C%20and%20enables%20us%20to%20deliver%20results.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EToday%2C%20we're%20rolling%20out%20new%20and%20enhanced%20tools%20to%20help%20you%20accelerate%20high%20performance%20and%20swiftly%20address%20low%20performance.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20a%20globally%20consistent%20and%20transparent%20experience%20for%20employees%20and%20managers%20(subject%20to%20local%20laws%20and%20consultation).%20These%20tools%20will%20also%20help%20foster%20a%20culture%20of%20accountability%20and%20growth%20by%20enabling%20you%20to%20address%20performance%20challenges%20with%20clarity%20and%20empathy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EManager%20Readiness%3A%20FY25%20Performance%2C%20Connect%20and%20Rewards%3A%20Register%20for%20a%2060-minute%20virtual%2C%20facilitated%20session%20to%20dive%20deeper%20into%20the%20performance%20landscape%20at%20Microsoft.%20Each%20session%20will%20explore%20what's%20new%20for%20FY25%20rewards%2C%20provide%20guidance%20on%20differentiating%20rewards%20outcomes%2C%20and%20define%20what%20it%20means%20to%20deliver%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20impact.%26quot%3B%20Next%20week%2C%20you'll%20also%20see%20a%20mail%20from%20Performance%20and%20Development%20to%20all%20employees%20with%20more%20details%20on%20Connects.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EClarity%20and%20Transparency%20in%20Rewards%3A%20This%20year%2C%20we'll%20ensure%20more%20transparency%20and%20clarity%20in%20the%20Rewards%20process%20for%20managers%20including%20additional%20guidance%20for%20each%20rewards%20outcome%20and%20showing%20payout%20percentages%20to%20help%20you%20make%20decisions%20that%20align%20with%20our%20high-performance%20expectations.%20More%20Rewards%20details%20will%20be%20shared%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EPerformance%20Improvement%20Process%3A%20If%20an%20employee%20is%20not%20meeting%20expectations%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20Performance%20Improvement%20Plan%20(PIP)%2C%20a%20new%20globally%20consistent%20approach%20to%20set%20clear%20expectations%20and%20a%20timeline%20for%20improvement.%20The%20employee%20can%20accept%20the%20improvement%20plan%20or%20choose%20to%20transition%20out%20of%20the%20company%20with%20the%20offer%20of%20a%20Global%20Voluntary%20Separation%20Agreement%20(GVSA).%20This%20performance%20improvement%20process%20is%20available%20year-round%20so%20you%20can%20act%20quickly%20to%20transparently%20address%20performance%20issues%2C%20while%20offering%20employees%20choice.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EUpdated%20Internal%20Movement%2FExternal%20Rehire%20Policy%3A%20Employees%20with%20zero%20and%2060%25%20Rewards%20outcomes%20and%2For%20on%20an%20active%20PIP%20will%20not%20be%20eligible%20for%20internal%20transfers.%20Former%20employees%20who%20left%20with%20zero%20or%2060%25%20Rewards%20or%20during%2Fafter%20a%20PIP%20will%20not%20be%20eligible%20for%20rehire%20until%20two%20years%20after%20their%20termination%20date.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EManager%20Excellence%20Initiatives%3A%20Additionally%2C%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20we'll%20launch%20several%20initiatives%20to%20strengthen%20how%20we%20measures%20manage%2C%20and%20motivate%20teams%20to%20deliver%20for%20our%20customers.%20You'll%20have%20access%20to%20scenario-based%2C%20Al-supported%20tools%20designed%20to%20help%20you%20prepare%20for%20constructive%20or%20challenging%20conversations%20by%20practicing%20in%20an%20interactive%20environment.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EThank%20you%20for%20your%20leadership%20and%20commitment%20to%20driving%20high%20performance%20and%20accountability%20across%20your%20team.%20This%20isn't%20just%20about%20Microsoft's%20success.%20This%20is%20about%20your%20success%2C%20your%20team's%20success%2C%20our%20customers'%20success%2C%20and%20together%2C%20fostering%20a%20culture%20where%20high-performing%2C%20winning%20teams%20can%20thrive.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aastewart%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eastewart%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%2B1-425-344-8242.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-email-details-new-policies-cull-low-performers-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insi