20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogle%20violated%20antitrust%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20monopolizing%20the%20digital%20advertising%20industry.%20The%20DOJ%20has%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20have%20Google%20divest%20Google%20Ad%20Manager%2C%20which%20is%20used%20for%20publishing%20and%20selling%20ads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289b9fae3-2633-4c0f-b160-a77ee2458acd%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBreaking%20up%20Chrome%20and%20Android%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20would%20experience%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20loss%26quot%3B%20if%20it%20had%20to%20separate%20its%20Chrome%20business%2C%20given%20all%20the%20data%20the%20search%20giant%20collects%20from%20search%20results%20and%20targeted%20advertising%20in%20Chrome%2C%20said%20Dave%20Heger%2C%20senior%20analyst%20at%20Edward%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20be%20surprised%20if%20it%20went%20all%20the%20way%20to%20forcing%20a%20separation%20of%20Chrome%2C%20but%20I%20do%20kind%20of%20wonder%20about%20the%20revenue%20sharing%20agreement%20and%20default%20browser%20if%20there%20would%20be%20some%20kind%20of%20focus%20on%20that%20kind%20of%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20Heger%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20Android%20generates%20revenue%20for%20Google%20in%20multiple%20ways%2C%20such%20as%20through%20the%20Play%20Store%20and%20by%20driving%20users%20to%20other%20Google%20services%20like%20search%2C%20YouTube%2C%20and%20Gmail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll-in-all%2C%20the%20divestiture%20of%20Chrome%20and%20possibly%20Android%20would%20detrimentally%20impact%20Google's%20ability%20to%20direct%20traffic%20on%20the%20desktop%20and%20mobile%20device%2C%20negatively%20impacting%20both%20revenues%2Fprofits%2C%26quot%3B%20Morgan%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8606da4-5cae-4fd2-b64b-673bd8a607b7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGoogle's%20search%20deal%20with%20Apple%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEnding%20the%20revenue-sharing%20agreement%20with%20Apple%20could%20save%20Google%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%20although%20it%20means%20Google%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20the%20default%20search%20engine%20for%20iPhone%20users%20and%20would%20be%20at%20a%20loss%20if%20Apple%20made%20a%20deal%20with%20another%20browser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20if%20fewer%20people%20use%20Google%2C%20it%20lessens%20the%20value%20of%20Google%20search%20as%20the%20company%20modifies%20its%20algorithms%20based%20on%20data%20it%20collects%20from%20users'%20search%20results.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20drives%20a%20lot%20of%20traffic%20when%20you%20think%20about%20how%20many%20people%20are%20doing%20searches%20on%20their%20phone%2C%26quot%3B%20Heger%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20certainly%20have%20an%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-case-chrome-android-sale-monopoly-doj-remedy-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745271537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6806b8723fe8d3928363a68d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-case-chrome-android-sale-monopoly-doj-remedy-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Google%20faces%20a%20crucial%20moment%20with%20the%20DOJ's%20remedy%20hearing.%20The%20DOJ%20has%20asked%20for%20Chrome%20and%20Android's%20separation%20due%20to%20antitrust%20violations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rmchan%40businessinsider.com%20(Rosalie%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A76%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-antitrust-case-chrome-android-sale-monopoly-doj-remedy-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22National%20ID%20cards%20of%20Hasina%2C%209%20family%20members%20'locked'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745271150000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-120497667%2Cimgsize-40042.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3