%3E%26quot%3BBorrowers%20who%20don't%20make%20payments%20on%20time%20will%20see%20their%20credit%20scores%20go%20down%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20their%20wages%20automatically%20garnished%2C%26quot%3B%20Education%20Secretary%20Linda%20McMahon%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fopinion%2Faccountability-returns-to-student-loans-forgiveness-borrower-debt-payment-9508da8d%3Fmod%3Dhp_opin_pos_2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20alongside%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20has%20not%20collected%20on%20defaulted%20student%20loans%20since%20March%202020%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20relief%20measures%20put%20in%20place%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20pandemic.%20Starting%20in%20May%2C%20the%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20office%20will%20restart%20the%20Treasury%20Offset%20Program%2C%20which%20withholds%20government%20benefits%2C%20including%20Social%20Security%20and%20tax%20refunds%2C%20from%20people%20with%20past-due%20payments.%20After%2030%20days%2C%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20would%20start%20garnishing%20wages%20for%20defaulted%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department's%20press%20release%20said%20that%20FSA%20will%20contact%20defaulted%20borrowers%20over%20the%20next%20two%20weeks%20to%20urge%20them%20to%20make%20plans%20to%20restart%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20a%20student%20borrower%20with%20a%20federal%20loan%20balance%20and%20haven't%20been%20making%20payments%2C%20you%20must%20restart%20payments%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20McMahon%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20office%20is%20providing%20every%20form%20of%20assistance%20we%20legally%20can%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20monthly%20payment%20can%20fit%20into%20your%20budget.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%205%20million%20student-loan%20borrowers%20are%20in%20default%2C%20or%20more%20than%20270%20days%20past%20due.%20The%20New%20York%20Federal%20Reserve%20recently%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener