52FNinja-NC301-placeholder-Cream-Maker%252Fdp%252FB08QXB9BH5%253Fth%253D1%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENinja%20Creami%20Ice%20Cream%20Maker%3C%2Fa%3E%20took%20TikTok%20by%20storm%3B%20our%20feeds%20blew%20up%20with%20custom%20vegan-friendly%2C%20dairy-free%20ice%20cream%20to%20protein-packed%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%26quot%3B%20frozen%20treats.%20I've%20tested%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20ice%20cream%20makers%20over%20the%20years%2C%20so%20I%20had%20to%20get%20my%20hands%20on%20the%20Creami%20and%20the%20new%20soft-serve%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15109102269fj-20%26h%3D824b613186ad39686187c6a0942fc94f41140c5e325dec06e144e64ecc501ec1%26postID%3D67f7e241b154b4859e6d90b4%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fninja-creami-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FNinja-Milkshake-Calories-Program-NC701%252Fdp%252FB0DSJW8SFG%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENinja%20Swirl%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20pint%20upon%20pint%20of%20frozen%20treats%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Ninja%20Creami%20is%20great%2C%20but%20not%20exactly%20a%20game-changer.%20Both%20the%20Creami%20and%20Swirl%20are%20great%20for%20people%20with%20dietary%20restrictions%20or%20who%20want%20to%20invent%20new%20recipes.%20Read%20on%20for%20my%20experience%20testing%20the%20Creami%20and%20Swirl%2C%20who%20should%20buy%20them%2C%20and%20what%20alternatives%20you%20may%20want%20to%20consider%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c74b2e5a-2880-43cf-832a-ca087b0d7567%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Getting%20started%5C%22%3EGetting%20started%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ninja%20Creami%20comes%20with%20the%20main%20unit%2C%20two%20pint%20containers%2C%20and%20a%20recipe%20book.%20I%20came%20into%20testing%20expecting%20my%2011-year-old%20son%20and%20I%20could%20just%20pop%20in%20the%20ingredients%20and%20have%20ice%20cream%20in%20minutes.%20Unfortunately%2C%20like%20many%20other%20countertop%20ice%20cream%20machines%2C%20there's%20a%20waiting%20period%3A%2024%20hours%20in%20the%20case%20of%20the%20Creami.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20is%20to%20create%20an%20ice%20cream%20mixture.%20Then%20you%20pour%20the%20concoction%20into%20one%20of%20the%20Ninja%20pint%20containers%20and%20freeze%20it%20for%2024%20hours.%20After%20it's%20frozen%20solid%2C%20you%20install%20the%20container%20in%20the%20machine's%20outer%20bowl%2C%20select%20the%20proper%20setting%2C%20and%20watch%20it%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b2a23e01-6725-4aaa-a653-cb1713ba1613%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ninja%20Creami%20review%5C%22%3ENinja%20Creami%20performance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Composite%20image%20showing%20a%20close-up%20of%20the%20Ninja%20Creami%20setting%20menu%20and%20the%20Creami%20in%20action%20making%20ice%20cream.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68069946c6ad288d147eb61b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou%20need%20to%20prep%20your%20mixture%20and%20freeze%20it%20for%2024%20hours%20before%20even%20getting%20to%20the%20Creamify%20part.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brain%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ninja%20Creami%20works%20by%20spinning%20the%20frozen%20ingredients%20for%20two%20to%20five%20minutes%2C%20which%20introduces%20air%20and%20gives%20the%20ice%20cream%20its%20texture.%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20loud%20the%20unit%20is.%20I%20held%20a%20sound%20meter%20nearby%2C%20and%20it%20registered%2080%20decibels%2C%20which%20is%20about%20as%20loud%20as%20heavy%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20attempts%20at%20making%20ice%20cream%20came%20out%20too%20soupy.%20It%20still%20tasted%20great%2C%20but%20the%20texture%20was%20off.%20After%20looking%20at%20the%20directions%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20needed%20to%20turn%20my%20freezer%20to%20its%20coldest%20setting.%20Also%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20you%20need%20to%20turn%20the%20machine%20on%20before%20installing%20the%20bowl.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20doesn't%20recognize%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20rarely%20a%20problem%20with%20my%20family%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20finish%20your%20pint%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20flatten%20the%20remainder%2C%20put%20the%20cover%20back%20on%2C%20and%20put%20it%20back%20in%20your%20freezer.%20When%20you're%20ready%20to%20eat%20it%20again%2C%20just%20run%20the%20same%20program%20you%20used%20originally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c96bc77c-fff9-4dda-a43c-ec6fb0b20a74%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ice%20cream%5C%22%3EIce%20cream%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222993%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close-up%20of%20the%20Ninja%20Creami%20ice%20cream%20pints%20with%20frozen%20mixtures.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680684983fe8d39283639d64%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222245%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20liked%20using%20the%20included%20recipe%20book%20as%20a%20guide%20for%20my%20Creami%20concoctions%20%E2%80%94%20I%20made%20lemon%20sorbet%20and%20cinnamon%20bun%20ice%20cream.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20the%20texture%20was%20way%20too%20soupy%20at%20first.%20Once%20I%20adjusted%20my%20freezer%20temperature%2C%20the%20resulting%20ice%20cream%20was%20excellent.%20I%20found%20it%20helped%20to%20run%20the%20respin%20feature%20after%20the%20initial%20spin%20to%20achieve%20the%20perfect%20texture.%20This%20adds%20about%20two%20minutes%20to%20the%20mixing%20time%2C%20but%20the%20results%20are%20creamier%20and%20less%20chalky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spinning%20the%20ice%20cream%2C%20you%20can%20add%20mix-ins%20by%20scooping%20out%20a%20hole%20that%20reaches%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20container.%20Then%2C%20you%20add%20cereal%2C%20cookies%2C%20chocolate%20chips%2C%20or%20