that%20promotes%20collaborative%20work%20between%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20spent%20eight%20years%20at%20The%20Carlyle%20Group%2C%20a%20private-equity%20firm%20with%20more%20than%20%24200%20billion%20in%20assets%20under%20managements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20native%20previously%20worked%20as%20Assistant%20Secretary%20and%20Under%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Treasury%20Department%20under%20President%20George%20H.W.%20Bush%20and%20as%20a%20lawyer%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%2C%20who%20is%20married%20with%20three%20children%2C%20has%20an%20BA%20in%20politics%20from%20Princeton%20University%20and%20a%20law%20degree%20from%20Georgetown%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b79f9ec8-e782-44ec-9103-ad5f6ac84b05%5C%22%3EPowell%20vs.%20Trump%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20both%20of%20Trump's%20terms%20in%20office%2C%20Powell%20has%20had%20to%20grapple%20with%20concerns%20of%20a%20slowing%20global%20economy%20and%20political%20pressure%20from%20the%20president%20to%20cut%20interest%20rates.%20Trump's%20latest%20tariff%20plans%20have%20added%20to%20the%20economic%20uncertainty%20and%20public%20fears%20of%20an%20impending%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-feud-federal-reserve-chair-jerome-powell-interest-rates-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeech%20at%20the%20Economic%20Club%20of%20Chicago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Powell%20said%20that%20tariffs%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration%20could%20create%20a%20%26quot%3Bchallenging%20scenario%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20economy%20and%20are%20likely%20to%20at%20least%20temporarily%20raise%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20warned%20that%20if%20tariffs%20drive%20up%20consumer%20prices%20and%20slow%20down%20overall%20economic%20growth%2C%20it%20could%20put%20the%20Fed's%20dual%20mandate%20%E2%80%94%20low%20unemployment%20and%20price%20stability%20%E2%80%94%20at%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20price%20stability%2C%20we%20cannot%20achieve%20the%20long%20periods%20of%20strong%20labor%20market%20conditions%20that%20benefit%20all%20Americans%2C%26quot%3B%20Powell%20said%20in%20his%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmagnificent-7-stock-value-loss-market-tank-nvidia-tariffs-fed-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPowell's%20speech%3C%2Fa%3E%20rattled%20investor%20confidence%20and%20deepened%20an%20ongoing%20stock%20sell-off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2257a58727-de7f-4319-9760-9717da56225c%5C%22%3ECan%20Trump%20fire%20Powell%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20Powell's%20speech%2C%20Trump%20attacked%20the%20Fed%20chair%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-media-technology-group-truth-social%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETruth%20Social%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20suggested%20to%20reporters%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20that%20he%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20remove%20Powell%20before%20his%20term%20is%20up%20%E2%80%94%20a%20position%20Trump%20also%20held%20during%20his%20first%20term%20in%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20want%20him%20out%2C%20he'll%20be%20out%20of%20there%20real%20fast%2C%20believe%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhite%20House%20economic%20advisor%20Kevin%20Hassett%20told%20reporters%20outside%20the%20White%20House%20the%20following%20day%20that%20the%20president%20and%20his%20team%20%26quot%3Bwill%20continue%20to%20study%26quot%3B%20if%20there's%20a%20way%20to%20fire%20Powell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Feconomy%2Fcentral-banking%2Ftrump-has-for-months-privately-discussed-firing-fed-chair-powell-628d3d79%3Fst%3DcS6MuX%26amp%3Breflink%3Darticle_copyURL_share%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20president%20has%20for%20months%20been%20privately%20talking%20about%20firing%20Powell%2C%20and%20has%20discussed%20replacing%20him%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-kevin-warsh-trump-fed-chair-replace-jerome-powell-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKevin%20Warsh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPowell%2C%20however%2C%20said%20in%20November%20after%20Trump%20was%20elected%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpowell-wont-resign-federal-reserve-step-down-trump-election-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiring%20the%20Fed%20Chair%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20against%20the%20law%2C%20and%20that%20he%20wouldn't%20resign%20if%20Trump%20asked%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20Economic%20Club%20that%20the%20Fed's%20%26quot%3Bindependence%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20law%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20in%20our%20statute%20that%20we're%20not%20removable%20except%20for%20cause.%26quot%3B%20And%20although%20Congress%20can%20change%20that%20law%2C%20Powell%20said%20he%20doesn't%20think%20it's%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20stipulates%20that%20a%20president%20can%20only%20fire%20a%20Fed%20official%20if%20there's%20cause%20for%20removal%2C%20and%20that%20doesn't%20include%20policy%20disagreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20central%20bank%20is%20supposed%20to%20operate%20independently%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Ffact-sheets%2F2025%2F02%2Ffact-sheet-president-donald-j-trump-reins-in-independent-agencies-to-restore-a-government-that-answers-to-the-american-people%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20expand%3C%2Fa%3E%20his%20presidential%20power%20over%20independent%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-jerome-powell-federal-reserve-chair%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745259