an%20borrowers'%20payments%20was%20a%20mistake%2C%20Trump's%20admin%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224562%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ed453869253ccddf9aff7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223041%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20clarified%20payment%20changes%20for%20married%20student-loan%20borrowers.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20corrected%20a%20filing%20that%20changed%20calculations%20for%20married%20student%20borrowers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20filing%20had%20said%20spousal%20income%20would%20be%20used%20to%20compute%20payments%2C%20even%20if%20they%20filed%20separately.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20department%20said%20the%20change%20was%20%26quot%3Berroneous%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20calculations%20would%20not%20change.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-married-student-loan-borrowers-higher-monthly-payments-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarried%20student-loan%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20changes%20that%20could%20increase%20their%20monthly%20payments%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20American%20Federation%20of%20Teachers%20sued%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration%20for%20taking%20down%20online%20access%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-blocked-income-driven-repayment-applications-save-plan-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincome-driven-repayment%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20wrote%20in%20a%20legal%20filing%20that%20married%20student-loan%20borrowers%20who%20file%20separate%20tax%20returns%20would%20have%20their%20combined%20income%20counted%20to%20calculate%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would've%20surged%20some%20borrowers'%20payments%20because%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20monthly%20payments%20on%20an%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%20would%20be%20based%20on%20a%20higher%20combined%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Education%20corrected%20that%20in%20a%20legal%20filing%20last%20week%2C%20saying%20the%20change%20to%20married%20borrowers'%20payment%20calculations%20%26quot%3Bwas%20erroneous.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20acting%20Undersecretary%20James%20Bergeron%20said%20that%20married%20borrowers%20filing%20separately%20would%20have%20the%20spouse%20counted%20in%20the%20family%20size%20to%20calculate%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%2C%20to%20be%20clear%2C%20the%20inclusion%20of%20a%20spouse%20for%20purposes%20of%20determining%20family%20size%20does%20not%20involve%20the%20consideration%20of%20spousal%20income%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20filing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20for%20now%2C%20the%20process%20for%20monthly%20payment%20calculations%20will%20stay%20the%20same%2C%20and%20married%20borrowers%20who%20file%20taxes%20separately%20do%20not%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20affording%20payments%20based%20on%20the%20combined%20spousal%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20department%20said%20it%20initially%20removed%20online%20access%20to%20income-driven-repayment%20applications%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Brequired%20consequence%26quot%3B%20of%20a%20federal%20court%20blocking%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E.%20SAVE%2C%20which%20was%20created%20by%20then-President%20Joe%20Biden%20to%20give%20borrowers%20lower%20monthly%20payments%20and%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20to%20debt%20relief%2C%20has%20been%20blocked%20since%20this%20past%20summer%20following%20a%20lawsuit%20from%20GOP-led%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20enrolled%20in%20SAVE%20are%20on%20administrative%20forbearance%20pending%20a%20final%20legal%20decision.%20They%20can%20choose%20to%20apply%20for%20a%20different%20repayment%20plan%20if%20they%20want%20to%20continue%20making%20payments%20and%20earning%20credit%20toward%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20not%20yet%20a%20timeline%20for%20when%20servicers%20will%20begin%20to%20process%20the%20backlog%20of%20income-driven-repayment%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20timeline%20is%20due%20to%20the%20servicers'%20internal%20procedures%2C%26quot%3B%20Bergeron%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BSpecifically%2C%20before%20servicers%20can%20begin%20to%20process%20applications%2C%20they%20must%20update%20the%20processing%20rules%20in%20their%20systems%20according%20to%20the%20terms%20of%20their%20contracts%20with%20Education.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20or%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-trump-clarifies-married-student-loan-borrowers-payments-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1745256238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68066d31a466d2b74ab3b33e%3Fformat%3Djpe